dict.acceptation: 发出…声音；变得；成为；处于…状态；
（牌戏、下棋等中）轮到的顺序；精力；干劲；（做某事的）尝试；

sent.orig: Kyong-go means a warning or half-point deduction and gam-jeom means a one-point deduction.
sent.trans: Kyoug-go是指一次警告或被扣减半分，gam-jeom是指被扣减1分。

sent.orig: From the get-go means from the beginning.
sent.trans: 原来fromtheget-go就是一开始的时候。

sent.orig: With the reduction of SRWC, GO activity decreased mild water stress and increased water stress.
sent.trans: 随着土壤相对含水量的下降，GO酶括性在土壤水分含量下降时首先降低，以后又逐渐上升。

sent.orig: We proved orthocompactness and weakly suborthocompactness are equivalent for all subspaces of product of two GO-space.
sent.trans: 证明了GO-空间子空间的正交紧性和弱子正交紧性是等价的。
